  <section>
    <p class="intro">
      "Nature Beyond Technology" explores the harmony between the natural world and human innovation. 
      Don Bonchaizer invites readers to rediscover the planet's untouched beauty while reflecting on how 
      technology can coexist with — rather than overpower — the environment.
    </p>

    <div class="feature-boxes">
      <div class="box">
        <h2>The Philosophy</h2>
        <p>An exploration of the balance between progress and preservation, urging a mindful approach to development.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="box">
        <h2>Natural Wonders</h2>
        <p>A celebration of landscapes, wildlife, and ecosystems that flourish far from the digital world.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="box">
        <h2>Human Connection</h2>
        <p>How grounding ourselves in nature helps restore creativity, clarity, and emotional well-being.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="about">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>Don Bonchaizer shares a lifelong passion for exploring nature’s untouched spaces. This project highlights the relationship between the natural world and sustainable technological progress.</p>
  </section>

